"     Nicholas Vogelzang, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?36/8/36999/contributors\">",
"     W Robert Lee, MD, MS, MEd",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?36/8/36999/contributors\">",
"     Jerome P Richie, MD, FACS",
